            "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363842522/image_1363842522.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"glowing graph 2\" data-id=\"1363842522\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1122px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363842522/image_1363842522.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363842522/image_1363842522.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363842522/image_1363842522.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363842522/image_1363842522.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363842522/image_1363842522.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363842522/image_1363842522.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363842522/image_1363842522.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1363842522/image_1363842522.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jonathan Kitchen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Breakingviews</em></p> <p>Capital-markets bankers started 2025 betting on an initial public offering boom. Now they’re facing a plot twist. Monday’s market selloff and surging volatility may give IPO hopefuls like Klarna (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KLAR\" title=\"Klarna\">KLAR</a>), CoreWeave (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CRWV\" title=\"CoreWeave, Inc.\">CRWV</a></p>",
